For this update we decided to completely redo the layout of the Dating page: We deleted excess buttons and increased the size of those frequently used We increased the page space with user photographs Now on the Dating page you can see the distance between yourself and other users. To do so you need to allow Topface access to your location We changed the icon displaying online status. Now you can see from which device a user has logged into Topface We ve also added many other improvements. In the last version we added the Bonus page so that you can earn free Coins in this one we added new tasks that are now even easier to complete.
In this version we ve completely redesigned the Photofeed corrected a few bugs and changed the Bonus Screen. Now you can earn free Coins for watching videos and completing tasks!
